commit.message:
feat: replace color text input with visual swatch picker

- HTML: 10 clickable circular swatches (×, Crimson, Tangerine, Lemon, Lime,
  Teal, Sky, Cobalt, Violet, Rose, White) with hidden input id=discColor
- CSS: --disc-{slug} OKLCH placeholder variables (Saul will override);
  .color-picker, .color-swatch, .color-swatch.selected, .color-none,
  .color-label, .disc-color-dot styles; ≥44px touch targets via ::after
- JS: setColorPicker() / resetColorPicker() helpers; picker click handler;
  openAddModal resets picker; openEditModal restores selected swatch;
  card renders colored 10px dot via var(--disc-{slug}) beside �� label

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
